The paper discusses a system for monitoring computer networks and improving situational awareness of network administrators through sonification. This topic falls under several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Software Engineering (cs.SD) as the system is a software tool, Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) as the system is used for network defence, Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) as the system deals with network traffic flows, Systems and Control (cs.SY) as the system involves monitoring and control of network behaviour, and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) as the system aims to improve the user experience of network administrators.
